{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"21":"Funerals (Kitab Al-Jana'iz)"},"section_detail":{"21":{"hadithnumber_first":3089,"hadithnumber_last":3241,"arabicnumber_first":3089,"arabicnumber_last":3241}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3096,"arabicnumber":3096,"text":"حدثنا احمد بن حنبل، حدثنا عبد الرحمن بن مهدي، عن سفيان، عن محمد بن المنكدر، عن جابر، قال كان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم يعودني ليس براكب بغل ولا برذون","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (5664)"}],"reference":{"book":21,"hadith":8}}]}